---
title: Yellow Squash Flatbreads with Melty Mozzarella, Pine Nuts, and a Chili Honey Drizzle
description: Although melty cheese is a must for any toasted flatbread (this one has a nice hunk of mozzarella), you also need some fresh, bright accents to cut through all that richness. We’re bringing in some yellow squash and scallions to add veggie savoriness, while basil adds an herbal touch and the chili honey garnish lends a whisper of spicy sweetness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/yellow-squash-flatbreads-d9d569e4.jpg
